  Locus:
    Page: 264
    Verse: 14
Tags:
  - Illusions
---
Truth is simple, but Illusion makes it infinitely intricate. The person is
rare who possesses an insatiable longing for Truth; the rest allow Illusion
to bind them ever more and more.
